You know what this reminds me of?
Did anyone else have the Crayola airbrush as a kid?
Put a felt marker in the end and turn on a little electric pump to blow the ink off the tip of the marker.
Stupid, simple, and highly unreliable, but still fun.

snippet.textDisplay: Hey Gav,  I think we in the audience are emotionally prepared to see a much more dark and dramatic slow Mo video.  Of course fake but I think we're ready to see you and Dan get shot up with bullets and blood gushing out and then fall to the ground dead.  Dramatically.  For the young kids of course at the end you both jump up and say "ha ha slowmo".  I think we're prepared to be shocked and then moved to tears to see your bullet riddled bodies fall to the ground. With blood gushing out.  At the end letting everybody know that you're OK.
